Testing plot generation code:

python3 -m venv plot_env
source plot_env/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt


Ensure all dependencies are installed correctly:

pip list

Ensure all the hardcoded paths inside the code for reading/generating files are as expected

Install language models for SpaCy:â€¨
python3 -m spacy download en_core_web_sm

Execute the code:

e.g.

nohup python3 reddit_comments.py &

Plot generation can take a fair amount of time so better to run it as a background job.

Some of the code reads CSV files. You can access these files at https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1FfImemej9bpH4RhEQSSEFQ4So4w6XFh7?usp=drive_link

We could not upload them here due to GitHub's size limit.

Please let us know in case you can't access the above Google Drive link and we will provide it to you.
